  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy of BGG492 in reducing the sensitivity to flashing
      lights of patients with photosensitive epilepsy, using EEG as a readout.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
